    "The crypto market offers 24 h trading throughout the year.",
    "In the existing traditional financial market, investors may hold assets for a short period of a few minutes (Glantz and Kissell 2013), and the crypto market is no different.",
    "Many online exchanges offer tools and services that enable cryptocurrency traders to trade for minutes or seconds, resulting in high profits (Brauneis et al. 2022; Chu et al. 2019).",
    "Moreover, compared to other financial instruments, cryptocurrencies demonstrate higher intraday volatility (movements of 3-5% are common), and a large portion of high-frequency trades are pursued through algorithmic trading bots, which signifies the use of high-frequency data in analyzing cryptocurrencies (Chan et al. 2022; Zhang et al. 2019b).",
